description: These face marks are laughing so hard they’re waving their arms as if to say “stop it, you’re killing me!” There is even a coffin with one of these emotes! This is the kind of laugh that comes from deep inside the belly and may even hurt. In fact, some of these emoticons legitimately look like they are in pain from laughing so hard.
